@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ihcmlr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.46 / wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.12)))
    tmp = 0.55
    v0 = (v1 * v2)
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v0 + 0.94)) + wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.13)))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.34) + (v2 + 0.44 * v1 + 0.94)) + (wp.exp(v0 + 0.41) - (v1 + 0.01 + v0 + 0.34)))
    v2 = (0.46 - wp.exp((v0 + 0.62 * v2 + 0.27)))
    data[tid] = v0
